			<div id="post-3533" class="hentry p3 post publish author-c4chaos category-open-practice category-spirituality y2009 m10 d24 h11">
				<h3 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.c4chaos.com/2009/10/the-science-of-enlightenment-consciousness-as-a-three-layered-cake/" title="Permalink to The Science of Enlightenment: Consciousness as a Three-Layered Cake" rel="bookmark">The Science of Enlightenment: Consciousness as a Three-Layered Cake</a></h3>
				<div class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2009-10-24T18:12:13+0000">Saturday, October 24th, 2009</abbr></div>
				<div class="entry-content">
<p>In my previous post I transcribed Session 13: Track 1 &#8211; The Pathless Land of The Science of Enlightenment series. In that talk Shinzen Young uses a metaphor of a &#8220;three-layered cake&#8221; to describe the journey from the surface of consciousness to the Source of consciousness. In this post I&#8217;ve transcribed the next two tracks [&hellip;]</p>
<p><span class='st_facebook_buttons' st_title='The Science of Enlightenment: Consciousness as a Three-Layered Cake' st_url='http://www.c4chaos.com/2009/10/the-science-of-enlightenment-consciousness-as-a-three-layered-cake/' displayText='share'></span><span class='st_twitter_buttons' st_title='The Science of Enlightenment: Consciousness as a Three-Layered Cake' st_url='http://www.c4chaos.com/2009/10/the-science-of-enlightenment-consciousness-as-a-three-layered-cake/' displayText='share'></span><span class='st_email_buttons' st_title='The Science of Enlightenment: Consciousness as a Three-Layered Cake' st_url='http://www.c4chaos.com/2009/10/the-science-of-enlightenment-consciousness-as-a-three-layered-cake/' displayText='share'></span><span class='st_sharethis_buttons' st_title='The Science of Enlightenment: Consciousness as a Three-Layered Cake' st_url='http://www.c4chaos.com/2009/10/the-science-of-enlightenment-consciousness-as-a-three-layered-cake/' displayText='share'></span><span class='st_fblike_buttons' st_title='The Science of Enlightenment: Consciousness as a Three-Layered Cake' st_url='http://www.c4chaos.com/2009/10/the-science-of-enlightenment-consciousness-as-a-three-layered-cake/' displayText='share'></span><span class='st_plusone_buttons' st_title='The Science of Enlightenment: Consciousness as a Three-Layered Cake' st_url='http://www.c4chaos.com/2009/10/the-science-of-enlightenment-consciousness-as-a-three-layered-cake/' displayText='share'></span></p>
